{"tid":1937402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當台灣人自稱自己係國民，我哋香港人又會係點？","createTime":"2020-03-22T01:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T22:07:13.000Z","uid":314617,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28152147b91b3cc2187b4fb1c17d8ef615e21070","tid":1937402,"uid":314617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T01:31:38.000Z","msg":"台灣地區使用「我國」、「國民」等詞近年變得好普遍，<br />\n就連官方同傳媒都有用，<br />\n變相間接認同自己中華民國係「XX」<br />\n（XX係乜，小弟在此不提）；<br />\n但係香港情況點樣？<br />\n當有人話「香港XX，唯一出路」嗰陣，<br />\n會唔會肯定自己係香港人？<br />\n<br />\n當然，民主係我哋自己去爭取嘅，<br />\n只要大家努力，<br />\n最終必會取得民主勝利。"},{"pid":"58767b56761bc621f56489c318a626843f0fd58d","tid":1937402,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T01:49:21.000Z","msg":"連上連登都斯斯縮縮，唔難想像你喺現實應該都係啲得把口係黃嘅人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9837e9a7e86f1f266ba9b579c10c4caa2470e05","tid":1937402,"uid":8483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58767b56761bc621f56489c318a626843f0fd58d","tid":1937402,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T01:49:21.000Z","msg":"連上連登都斯斯縮縮，唔難想像你喺現實應該都係啲得把口係黃嘅人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"連打獨立兩隻字都要打XX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2177ae604c074b19f32fb8203da476e450794f77","tid":1937402,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民族自強，香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"322ec2b59c9140f36074448d7a89de1882f74e86","tid":1937402,"uid":314617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9837e9a7e86f1f266ba9b579c10c4caa2470e05","tid":1937402,"uid":8483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58767b56761bc621f56489c318a626843f0fd58d","tid":1937402,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T